      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "1t is said today that the Graves\n. interests have renewed their offers\nto buy out the interests of the\nWashington Water Power Co. The\noffer was made some time ago, Or\niginally, but was turned down. The\nlast few days negotiations have\nbeen opened up again. 1t is said\nthat the only hitch in the deal now\nis that the Washington Water\nPower Co. wants to turn over lot\nof old junk for new and the Graves\npeople won't close the deal on that\naccount."
    }
